{
  "id": "adv_bond_rei_01_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ん～、おいひい～！\nじゃあ次は、チョコ味にしようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm~‚ delicious~!\nThen next‚ let's do chocolate flavor",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8453.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、大きなマカロンですね。お煎餅くらいある\n差し入れでもらったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's a big macaron. About the size of a rice cracker\nDid you get any snacks?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.033333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、今日の現場でね。沙季も食べる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ at the scene today. Do you want to eat‚ Saki?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、悪いですよ。怜ちゃんの大好物ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No-no‚ that's not on. That's Rei-chan's favorite food",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "独り占めするほど食い意地張ってないわよ\nこころやすずじゃないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to eat it all by myself\nI'm not comfortable with it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、沙季の好きな食べ物って知らないわね\n何が好きなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ I don't know what Saki's favorite food is\nWhat do you like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "『くさや』ですね\n公式のプロフィールにも載せていますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's \"Kusaya\"\nIt's also on my official profile",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "くさや……そういえば書いてあったような……\nどんな食べ物なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kusaya… you mention it‚ it seems like it was written down…\nWhat kind of food is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "魚の干物ですね。発酵食品なこともあり、栄養豊富で\nカルシウムはアジのヒラキの二十倍もあるそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's dried fish. It's also fermented food‚ so it's rich in nutrients\nIt is said to contain 20 times more calcium than grilled horse mackerel",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、疲労回復効果に抗菌作用もあって\n一部の地域では、薬のかわりにもなっていたそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Additionally‚ it has fatigue recovery and antibacterial effects\nIn some areas‚ it was used as a substitute for medicine",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "へ～、健康的でいいじゃない。一度食べてみたいわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heh~‚ that sounds healthy and good. I'd like to try it sometime!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　では、今度用意しますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? Then I'll prepare it next time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9666632335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――数日後",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、何この匂い！？\n無理！　ほんとに無理っ、それ以上近づけないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ what's that smell?\nNo way! Really no way‚ don't get any closer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2333334606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "酷いです、怜ちゃん……！\n食べてくれるって言ったじゃないですか……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so sad‚ Rei-chan…!\nYou said you'd eat it…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2333334606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "まだ事務所に入ったばかりの頃\n琴乃ちゃん達に出したら、とても不評で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I first joined the agency\nI gave it to Kotono-chan and the others‚ and they complained a lot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7333334606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "それ以来、食べる時は一人でこっそり食べたり\nわざわざ実家に帰ったり、ずっと気を遣って――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From then on‚ I would sneak out and eat alone‚\nreturn to my parents' house on purpose‚ always be considerate――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0666667939,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7033.3332060999965
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9899.999872799996
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12033.333206099996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "――って、怜ちゃん！　待って下さい！\n一口だけでも、はい、あーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Hey‚ Rei-chan! Wait a minute!\nJust one bite‚ okay‚ ahhhー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1333334607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "いや～～～～～～～～～～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No~~~~~~~~~~~~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.9000052137,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}